values:
jeez, we dont like that
weather one bit.

oh no. oh no. oh no.
ohhhhh no.

hey, can you hand me a
blanket?

no thats not just you,
its cold.

ok. new plan. grab a
bigger coat.

know anyone willing to
lend us a hot tub?

gather round the fire,
so you dont freeze.

shivering is nothing
to be embarrased of
